            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="entry-dates">Aug 2021 - May 2024</div>
        </div>

        <div class="entry">
          <div class="entry-details">
            <div class="entry-title">Fiscal Affairs Council</div>
            <div class="entry-subtitle">Chair of Annual Budget, Chair of Investment Task Force</div>
