              <li>Researched alternative investment vehicles for Fiscal portfolio before adopting money market accounts</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="entry-dates">Aug 2021 - May 2022</div>
        </div>

        <div class="section-header">
          <h2 id="projects"><span class="section-icon">📊</span> Selected Projects</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="entry">
          <div class="entry-details">
            <div class="entry-title">Retailer Performance Analysis</div>
            <div class="entry-subtitle">Leveraging R for retailer process improvement and inventory strategy</div>
