              <li>Developed R Shiny dashboard for stakeholders to visualize seasonal trends and adjust inventory strategies</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="entry">
          <div class="entry-details">
            <div class="entry-title">Airbnb Location Breakdown</div>
